    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a world where every creak of the floorboard could be your last. In <i>Phantom's Estate</i>, you and your team of paranormal investigators are thrust into haunted locations to uncover the truth about restless spirits. Armed with your wits, specialized equipment, and a dose of courage, you'll explore eerie environments, gather clues, and attempt to solve the mystery before you become the hunted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware—the deeper you dig, the more dangerous it becomes. The spirits lurking in these haunted estates are far from friendly. As your sanity slips away, the world around you warps, twisting the lines between reality and the paranormal. The lower your sanity, the more aggressive the spirits get, until you find yourself not just investigating a haunting, but surviving one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to identify the ghost and escape with your life, or will you become just another tragic story on the estate's long list of victims?</p>",
